-- Brazil’s Eike Batista to Sell Energy Company MPX, Veja Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   M a l i n o w s k i
-- 2013-02-16T13:39:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-16/brazil-s-eike-batista-to-sell-energy-company-mpx-veja-says.html
Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista 
plans to sell his controlling stake in energy company  MPX ,
magazine Veja columnist Lauro Jardim reported.  The most likely buyer is Germany’s  E.ON , Jardim reported,
without saying where he obtained the information.  A spokeswoman for Batista’s holding company couldn’t
immediately provide comment when contacted by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Malinowski in Brasilia at 
 mmalinowski@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net . 